{"pages": [{"words": {"text": ["Pikes", "Peak", "Opera", "League", "Membership", "Application/Renewal", "Form", "PLEASE", "RENEW", "MEMBERSHIP:", "Membership", "fees", "are", "for", "the", "PPOL", "fiscal", "and", "program", "year", "of", "September", "1", "to", "August", "31", "each", "year.", "RENEW", "by", "JULY", "15", "to", "be", "included", "in", "Directory", "and", "to", "be", "sure", "that", "you", "continue", "to", "be", "on", "mailing", "and", "email", "communication", "lists.", "The", "Dues", "are", "$40", "for", "individuals", "and", "$60", "for", "couples/families", "and", "remain", "the", "same", "as", "in", "the", "previous", "5", "years.", "Your", "Dues", "go", "to", "help", "underwrite", "and", "pay", "performers", "for", "our", "excellent", "quality", "programming.", "These", "vocalists", "and", "performers", "need", "our", "support", "now", "more", "than", "ever.", "Also,", "there", "will", "be", "some", "programs", "and", "events", "that", "are", "for", "members", "only", "or", "open", "to", "members", "first.", "Additionally,", "if", "you", "are", "interested", "and", "can", "support,", "even", "a", "part,", "of", "a", "program", "or", "event", "for", "this", "coming", "year,", "please", "let", "us", "know", "as", "that", "helps", "defray", "venue", "and", "programming", "costs.", "Please", "PRINT", "information", "as", "is", "currently", "accurate", "for", "you", "even", "if", "the", "same", "as", "last", "year,", "inclusive", "of", "best", "phone", "#s", "and", "accurate", "email", "and", "mailing", "addresses", "to", "be", "assured", "that", "you", "will", "receive", "all", "updates", "and", "communications.", "An", "accurate", "database", "is", "crucial", "for", "these", "communications", "and", "keeping", "you", "informed.", "Name:", "_____________________________________________________", "Address:", "___________________________________________________", "(Please", "include", "FULL", "ADDRESS", "with", "city,", "state", "and", "zip", "code