 assured that you", "will receive all updates and communications. An accurate database is crucial for these", "communications and keeping you informed.", "Name: _____________________________________________________", "Address: ___________________________________________________", "(Please include FULL ADDRESS with city, state and zip code)", "Home Phone: ________________ Cell/Work Phone: _______________", "E-\u00ad\u2010mail: ____________________________________________________", "(PLEASE PRINT)", "Membership Category: Individual $40 ______ Couple/family $60 ______", "I would like to sponsor a program to further assist vocalists:", "_____ $50 _____ $100 _____ $150 $______ (write in amount)", "Volunteer by checking your areas of interest:", "Fund Raising ____ Young Voice Competition ____ Hospitality ____ Concierge Call Team ____", "Mailings ___ Special Events ___ Publicity ___ Membership ___ Greeter ___ Gift Baskets ____", "Distribution Directory ____IT ___ Graphic arts____ Membership Name Tags _____", "Make checks payable to PPOL; mail payment along with form to: Pikes Peak Opera League, P.O.", "Box 38478, Colorado Springs, CO 80937-\u00ad\u20108478.", "You may also renew online at pikespeakoperaleague.org under Membership tab with PayPal", "link. Please be sure that we have all your contact information.", "Thank you for your membership and support!"], "bbox": [[0.239347, 0.082659, 0.622922, 0.021455], [0.147843, 0.12618, 0.7378560000000001, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.144664, 0.7440610000000001, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.163149, 0.565852, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.181634, 0.740969, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.200119, 0.708691, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.218604, 0.7558499999999999, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.237089, 0.7607790000000001, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.255574, 0.037825, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.274058, 0.761083, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.292543, 0.680429, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.329513, 0.702277, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.347998, 0.7408809999999999, 0.018496], [0.147843, 0.366483, 